sec.p:
We performed phenotypic assays to screen for repurposing drugs that inhibit the replication and the cytopathic effects of virus infection. A derivative of the Broad repurposing library was used to incubate Caco-2 cells before infecting them with an isolate of SARS-CoV-2 (FFM-1 isolate, see
37
). Survival of cells was assessed using a cell viability assay and measured by high-content imaging using the Operetta CLS platform (PerkinElmer). Details of the drug repurposing screening are described in the supplemental material.
